    He funded the development of the Hydra chess computer in the 2000s, one of the most advanced AI-driven chess engines of its time.
- **Martial Arts & Fitness:**  
    A known Brazilian jiujitsu enthusiast, Tahnoun has been instrumental in promoting the sport in the UAE and frequently surrounds himself with world-class athletes.
- **Privacy and Low Profile:**  
    Despite his immense influence, he remains a relatively low-profile figure, rarely making public statements and preferring to operate behind the scenes.

